                <td>Ingredient 2 (e.g., Tomato Sauce)</td>
                <td>1 cup</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Ingredient 3 (e.g., Parmesan Cheese)</td>
                <td>1/4 cup</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Ingredient 4 (e.g., Basil)</td>
                <td>Fresh leaves for garnish</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <p><strong>Steps:</strong></p>
    <ol>
        <li>Cook the pasta according to package instructions.</li>
        <li>Heat the tomato sauce in a pan.</li>
        <li>Drain the cooked pasta and add it to the sauce, tossing to coat.</li>
        <li>Serve the pasta topped with Parmesan cheese and garnished with fresh basil.</li>
    </ol>

   
